{"tid":2243550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"麥當勞中國CEO：中國抗疫成效顯著 今年最少新開430家餐廳","createTime":"2020-10-14T23:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T07:49:54.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"131413feb189d1f8e7dc5ac4ce22de28528ca253","tid":2243550,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T23:14:15.000Z","msg":"麥當勞中國CEO：中國抗疫成效顯著 今年最少新開430家餐廳<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1602662752614&amp;issue=20201014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1602662752614%26issue%3D20201014&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=0663900a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1602662752614&amp;issue=20201014</a><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情對餐飲業造成衝擊，但麥當勞中國CEO張家茵接受內媒《中新社》訪問時表示，麥當勞中國不僅沒有縮減門店的計劃，更打算繼續在華大幅擴張。<br />\n<br />\n張家茵指，今年麥當勞中國在華的開店計劃沒有變化，今年至少新開430家餐廳，招聘18萬名員工。張表示，麥當勞中國之所以能夠繼續在中國擴張門店，並保持原來的戰略計劃，主要得益於中國對新冠肺炎疫情控制取得的顯著成效。疫情讓麥當勞對中國市場更有信心。"},{"pid":"8b07afc29b2ad5f941bdbf64b3a02a3803146261","tid":2243550,"uid":183758,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T23:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpVrjqH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpVrjqH.gif&h=26740ba1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f70451ac2958f8690ef3b0e26b5610f99a3ca5dd","tid":2243550,"uid":155095,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T23:30:39.000Z","msg":"麥當勞係美帝國品牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國人要支持真功夫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/81237893_607021250109531_5723598432262684672_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=Hm7ckWYl-ZgAX8Mj_5V&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=1b549ca98da56ca1a7394b